Description: Ion Alkaline Water LLC is the first retail alkaline water store in North America.
Full Description: Ion Alkaline Water LLC is the first retail alkaline water store in North America.     “Mandeville Louisiana was not my first choice, the store was to open three years ago in Maui Hawaii.”     I am going to write you as a man about my life and present business. I will try to avoid all of the enticing self-promoting egos, visions of grandeur, innuendos, and flowery promises normally laced in proposals. I retired out of the construction/home improvement industry over 20 years ago. My company had over 5000 employees and subcontractors in five states. I know how to expand, manage, and grow a business with multiple locations.      Two years ago while living in Maui my wife was diagnosed with pancreatic cancer. With a 96% death rate they naturally took her home to Mandeville. This brave woman turned down chemotherapy and radiation making her possibly the rarest survivor in the world. She will tell you that Ion Alkaline Water is a huge part of her recovery.     I have never been more passionate about anything in my life as I am about Ion Alkaline Water. At 67 I hope to do this quicker than the 25 years it took me to grow the construction business. I have five new locations that I personally plan to open this calendar year.     Mandeville Louisiana was a real retail challenge for several reasons. The people are full of life and very friendly but the state is not known for its healthy lifestyle choices ranking third in the nation for obesity. It is rated at number 44 for the lowest income levels, and 45th on education levels. I personally thrive on challenges, yes I spent some money, learned a lot and the store was a huge success its very first year.     Their Ion Alkaline Water purifiers generate a huge profit revenue stream of 3 to 5 hundred percent; but it was the rental market that I established that bridged the gaps, and every rental unit turned onto a sale within six months. They are the future of all world water.
Industry Groups: Commerce and Shopping, Health Care, Natural Resources, Sports

The network saw senior politicians, company directors, private bankers, business analysts, senior lawyers, hollywood film producers, television & radio presenters, entrepreneurs and thousands more joining before even public launch. The network is aiming to open for public registration by the end of September 2013. SuitLink offers its members the opportunity to connect with others, share thoughts, ideas and concepts, promote their companies and services, job seek and recruit, meet new friends and much more too.

Description: Trading price action using low risk
Full Description: TradersHelpDesk is the complete support desk for all traders, beginning and experienced.  THD follows The Wyckoff Common Sense Approach to Trading and specialize in teaching the skills that help you trade successfully, any markets include Stocks, Futures, Forex, Commodities ETF, Bonds or Indices. Education starts with identifying low risk entry points, high probability price patterns, trends, stops, profit targets and a written trading plan unique to your style of trading. By applying these, and a simple, yet effective methodology, we consistently and profitably take advantage of the markets.  THD free live trading room provides, free education and training sessions on the live edge of the market. In THD live trading room, we focus on markets that move. This means that we trade markets that we have identified as having enough volatility for the average trader to make money. Then we add a methodology that only allows us to enter on a low risk entry. (This typically means we enter with a risk of 8 ticks or less.) This methodology helps to protect our accounts during the inevitable drawdown periods. And to grow our account, we have a minimum of 1:2 Risk to Reward ratio. This means that for every $1.00 of risk we expect to make a minimum of $2.00.  If you are new to trading or can't find an edge in trading these sessions are very useful.

Description: Share and discover with people nearby.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Membo is a location-based discovery app that connects people within a 7 mile radius to surface and share the best events, places and activities in the area.  Different topics are published by Membo to the ‘Pulse’ section regularly, ranging in subject from “Best Spots to Take a Tinder Date” to  "Trends That Need To Die ASAP,” to encourage collaboration and discussion with local flavor. Users gain upvotes for their contributions, helping them earn status within Membo as a Tastemaker and a place on the Leaderboard. Tastemakers compete for top spot by posting only the best of the best, leaving the community with exciting, locally curated insights. Outside of the Pulse section, people further connect with one another in ‘Shout,’ a free-form chat environment, and get exclusive offers and deals in ‘Spots’ - a feed of nearby businesses and points of interest powered by Foursquare. Merchants are able to post offers to Membo for free.
Industry Groups: Apps, Other, Software, Travel and Tourism
Founders: Colin Pace, Sanjeev Malaney, Will Reeves
